OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1778613067
OL,3,CMan jailed for importing cocaine
OL,4,Ccandles under fake name
OL,6,FA Stockport man has been jailed after
OL,7,Fimporting candles into Jersey, which
OL,8,Fhid nearly 60 grams of cocaine.
OL,10,FBenjamin Jake Bartlett Noble, 24, was
OL,11,Fsentenced to three years and four
OL,12,Fmonths in prison by the island's Royal
OL,13,FCourt after attempting to smuggle the
OL,14,FClass A drug through the postal system.
OL,16,FJersey Customs officers seized a
OL,17,Fpackage at Postal Headquarters on
OL,18,FMonday 22 July 2024, which was
OL,19,Faddressed to 'Sue Cooper' in St Helier.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1778613067
OL,3,CMan jailed for importing cocaine
OL,4,Ccandles under fake name
OL,6,FHowever, the name was fake and two of
OL,7,Fthe three candles in the parcel had
OL,8,Fbeen hollowed out to conceal cocaine
OL,9,Fwith a total street value of #14,300.
OL,11,FOfficers used a search warrant at the
OL,12,FSt Helier address and initially
OL,13,Farrested Bartlett Noble, who denied
OL,14,Fall knowledge of the delivery -
OL,15,Fdespite an audio recording of him
OL,16,Fcontacting the post office and paying
OL,17,Ffor the package to be resent to the
OL,18,Fproperty.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1778613067
OL,3,CMan jailed for importing cocaine
OL,4,Ccandles under fake name
OL,6,FBartlett Noble's phone also showed
OL,7,FInternet searches related to the
OL,8,Fparcel's tracking number.
OL,10,FBartlett Noble was released and moved
OL,11,Fto the UK while the investigation was
OL,12,Fongoing, before being rearrested in
OL,13,FCamborne, Cornwall, in January this
OL,14,Fyear.
OL,16,FHe was charged back in Jersey and
OL,17,Ffirst denied importing the drugs,
OL,18,Flater pleading guilty.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
