FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1778613067
OL,3,CMan jailed for importing cocaine
OL,4,Ccandles under fake name
OL,6,FThe 24-year-old then claimed the plan
OL,7,Fwas for him to receive the package and
OL,8,Fhand it over to an unnamed third party.
OL,10,FPaul Le Monnier, Senior Manager at
OL,11,FJersey Customs and Immigration Service
OL,12,F(JCIS), explains: "This was a fairly
OL,13,Fsophisticated attempt to import
OL,14,Fcocaine through the postal system.
OL,16,F"Despite Bartlett Noble's best efforts
OL,17,Fto evade prosecution, he has now been
OL,18,Fsentenced for his role in the
OL,19,Fimportation.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
