PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1778613067
OL,3,CMan jailed for importing cocaine
OL,4,Ccandles under fake name
OL,6,F"JCIS continue to work closely with
OL,7,FJersey Post and law enforcement
OL,8,Fpartners to disrupt those who attempt
OL,9,Fto exploit postal services to import
OL,10,Fdrugs into Jersey."
